data.description: Welcome! To this turn key home with property galore! This beautiful place offers 5 acres of property for all the fun things! Outside you'll find a 30 x 40 ft Pole Barn with a Cement Pad, Electric & Water! Just wait there is more! The 2nd story has a tremendous amount of space for storage or additional needs. Walking into this home, there are 3 carpeted Bedrooms, featuring a Bonus Room to use as an office, den, craft room, etc. Both Bathrooms are fully updated! Stainless Steel Kitchen Appliances, LVT Flooring, Fresh Paint & Modern touches throughout this stunning home!  Newer Septic System, New Sump Pump. Call for a private showing, this home is a must see!
